{"tid":1620310,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"法治是保障自由、民主及公義之基礎，而政府用緊急法破壞法治，人民就有權利，也有義務推翻這個政府","createTime":"2019-10-04T10:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T12:47:41.000Z","uid":88263,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d621ed8264db4ae89f18d6b13e5661271abb8c83","tid":1620310,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:03:02.000Z","msg":"法治為何重要？<br />\n法治是保障自由、民主及公義之基礎。然而法治並非極權政府如中共、港共口中單指人民要守法。法治是法律本身是最高管治者，不論人民及政府都需要守法，而非極權政府管治人民的工具。唯有法律能夠管治政府及人民的時候，人民的自由方可獲得保障；當人民享有自由，方能實現真正的民主；當實現真正的民主，人民方可安居樂業。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;  <em>一位連登仔對法治的看法</em><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n我們認為下面這些真理是不證自明的：人人生而平等，造物主賦予他們若干不可剝奪的權利，其中包括生命權、自由權和追求幸福的權利。<span style=\"color: blue;\">為了保障這些權利，人們才在他們之間建立政府，而政府之正當權力，則來自被統治者的同意。</span>任何形式的政府，只要破壞上述目的，人民就有權利改變或廢除它，並建立新政府；新政府賴以奠基的原則，得以組織權力的方式，都要最大可能地增進民眾的安全和幸福。的確，從慎重考慮，不應當由於輕微和短暫的原因而改變成立多年的政府。過去的一切經驗也都說明，任何苦難，只要尚能忍受，人類都寧願容忍，而無意廢除他們久已習慣了的政府來恢復自身的權益。<span style=\"color: blue;\">但是，當政府一貫濫用職權、強取豪奪，一成不變地追逐這一目標，足以證明它旨在把人民置於絕對專制統治之下時，那麼，人民就有權利，也有義務推翻這個政府，並為他們未來的安全建立新的保障。</span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<em>美國獨立宣言</em><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8f9207ed6bf8aa865b57cb7c8a56b8ee7a9dcb26","tid":1620310,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:09:40.000Z","msg":"戴耀廷提出嘅法治四層次<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<em>有法可依、有法必依、以法限權、以法達義</em><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7d75ec2ca8d78b427b1eb1f00ef39d4b534e072a","tid":1620310,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:13:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffd4dc1815683dbddc5436be6975589d5e92bfa","tid":1620310,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:13:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548630f4a86e81514c57f90d7a626284274a0a31","tid":1620310,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:20:29.000Z","msg":"推法治啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c62559ccb3c26f7c816ac0a9330a1eaac0a3ca7","tid":1620310,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n真正的法治，是公義之治，由保障公民基本權利和自由的法律來管治統治者與被統治者，必須包括有效運行的獨立司法體系、司法救濟制度、違憲審查（司法覆核）制度，必須包括廉潔專業、學養倶豐、邏輯縝密、不偏不倚的法律專業人士（審、檢、辯）及其養成制度、甄選制度、培訓制度、監督制度、懲戒制度、職業保障制度。刑事審判必須奉行罪刑法定原則、罪刑不溯及既往原則、罪刑相當原則、證據裁判原則、無罪推定原則、罪疑唯有利於被告原則。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%A2%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E8%B6%8A%E4%BE%86%E8%B6%8A%E9%81%A0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E8%25B6%258A%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25B6%258A%25E9%2581%25A0%2F&d=x%2FNl6Ahg6Nkeqb8F8iTJG6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=9afacfd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E8%25B6%258A%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25B6%258A%25E9%2581%25A0%2F&h=b1e2b731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%A2%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E8%B6%8A%E4%BE%86%E8%B6%8A%E9%81%A0/</a>"},{"pid":"23045e080581dbe3e03862ae9f02454b53b83210","tid":1620310,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:27:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n法治是政治概念<br />\n<br />\n首先，法治是一個治理原則(a principle of governance)，是有關政府如何管治的問題。今日好多人見到法治，以為是一個法律概念，所以要找律師來請教；然後又有一些保守的律師團體出來叫人不要犯法，說律師的專業令他們要來捍衛法治。但都攪錯了！法治是一個管治問題，所以更加是一個政治概念。<br />\n<br />\n這個政治概念不是用來規範人民，而是用來規範實行管治的政府。簡單而言，政府用法律規範人民，而法治則用來規範政府。所以法治社會，說的不是人民守不守法，而是政府有沒有服從法治的原則。明乎此，就知道人民只能違反法律，但違反不了法治，因為法治屬於管治的領域。人民不是管治者，又如何破壞法治？<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1030253\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1030253&d=x%2FNl6Ahg6Nkeqb8F8iTJG6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=a18949e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1030253&h=fdc4a648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1030253</a>"},{"pid":"7b860263d2ef827776d49718d03c9e904aba7f23","tid":1620310,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n2004年，聯合國公佈對法治的定義，即所有人、機構和國家必須向法律負責。法律不僅須符合國際人權標準，更要公開頒布，由獨立一方作裁判，平等執行。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">但法治不只是依法辦事，更要確保三權分立、民眾要有決策參與權、法律要肯定、不能夠任意、程序要透明等。</span><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://app3.rthk.hk/special/pau/article.php?aid=725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp3.rthk.hk%2Fspecial%2Fpau%2Farticle.php%3Faid%3D725&d=x%2FNl6Ahg6Nkeqb8F8iTJG6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=f06a7a8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://app3.rthk.hk/special/pau/article.php?aid=725</a>"},{"pid":"7b0096f7930c723df24cf1a5b4061ab372f9ec89","tid":1620310,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n「法治」是指一些基本法律原則，這些原則規限在香港行使權力的方式。法治一詞具有多個不同的涵義和推論，其主要涵義是政府和所有公務人員的權力均來自表述於法例和獨立法院的判決中的法律。香港的政府系統內貫徹著一個原則，就是任何人（包括行政長官）除非有法律根據，否則不可以作出構成法律過失或會影響他人人身自由的行為。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.doj.gov.hk/chi/legal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.doj.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Flegal%2F&d=x%2FNl6Ahg6Nkeqb8F8iTJG6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=e572b05d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.doj.gov.hk/chi/legal/</a>"},{"pid":"2295bd2400aa43bb70c8de4e8efa70f31de32efe","tid":1620310,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}